{"tid":859561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"落手落腳去消滅香港人呢個族群","createTime":"2018-10-12T15:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T09:04:47.000Z","uid":177089,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"73c99a468cfcbfeb7841393fbc7cd5fdd3f02593","tid":859561,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:17:05.000Z","msg":"起高鐵 起大橋 加強對香港嘅人口運輸效率<br />\n每日150 對香港進行人口換血 降低香港生活質素<br />\n普教中 令香港下一代唔再講廣東話 可以北上居住<br />\n大灣區計劃 令香港人受唔住香港環境之後 北上居住<br />\n人工島 增加香港新移民居住空間 <br />\n<br />\n全個計劃 就係令香港人分散 搬上大陸 瓦解中共最驚嘅一班人 點解中共驚？<br />\n因為香港係英國前殖民地 有自由民主思想 呢啲係支那其他地方無嘅野 可以話香港真係反共嘅第一前線<br />\n<br />\n中共要令香港再無香港人 計劃已經到達中段 <br />\n被消滅 或者用最大力度反抗 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你會點揀？</span></span>"},{"pid":"b6c40b21c70e8ac39a062b3d84b920abb9c4df47","tid":859561,"uid":191352,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:21:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a462e7166d20044d90a9ea0e7b3d8509c8b1468f","tid":859561,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbe979e23aec547b4658fe1b383719bf6cd9b88","tid":859561,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:00:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc335ace5dfa566de89c69914a34b4e87a264342","tid":859561,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fbe979e23aec547b4658fe1b383719bf6cd9b88","tid":859561,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:00:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:04:47.000Z","msg":"自由係傳染病"}]}